{"tid":1433324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已FC方仲賢屋企被搜查超過一小時","createTime":"2019-08-08T12:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:12:04.000Z","uid":269785,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"333419cd165759d066d65df5c4dd91fa44a4bb19","tid":1433324,"uid":269785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，警方在方仲賢獲釋前約半小時，到方仲賢住所搜查逾一小時。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n方仲賢目前仍在明愛醫院留醫，明日傍晚將會見記者交代詳細情況。警方今日下午舉行記者會時亦預告，警方針對方仲賢的調查仍在進行中，方仲賢目前仍在醫院留醫，警方在他接受治療和完成初步調查後，計劃會先讓他擔保外出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%B2%E8%B3%A2%E5%82%8D%E6%99%9A%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E6%9A%AB%E6%9C%AA%E8%A2%AB%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88-%E4%BB%8D%E7%95%99%E9%86%AB%E6%98%8E%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E5%2582%258D%25E6%2599%259A%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2586%25AB%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%2F&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9f%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=d9f27e99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E5%2582%258D%25E6%2599%259A%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2586%25AB%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%2F&h=e94c8f28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%